title: Welcome to the Marks and Spencer dashboard catalogue

panels.content:
![kibana](img/mns.png) 

 ### Welcome to Integration Kibana Dashboards. 
Glad you could make it. Happy to have you here! 
##### Requirements
* **A good browser**  


 
##### What do we have here
*  We have a set of prebuilt dashboards per environment:

 1. [dev](index.html#/dashboard/file/integration_dev.json).
 2. [st](index.html#/dashboard/file/integration_st.json).
 3. [inta](index.html#/dashboard/file/integration_inta.json).

 *And oh !!! The dashboards for the other environments are Yet to come...*

 *And Also !!! If the dashboards are empty it is because that environment does not have data yet.*
